# Build-context filter for images built from the REPO ROOT (currently only
# peripheral/email/Dockerfile → the singleton mail-router service). Allowlist style:
# without this, `make mail-up` would ship the whole repo
# (~2GB: .venv-cua, .git, state/) to the daemon on every build.
# NB: orchestration/Dockerfile.control builds from context `orchestration` and
# is NOT affected by this file.
*
!peripheral/
!orchestration/
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
